can anything be done to reduce a dogs nipple size we rescued a dog that was used for breeding and her nipples are very large and very long is there anything we can do to reduce size she has been spayed and that has not helped shrink them at all you and i have been in the same boat i adopted a dog on june nd who was used for breeding over and over and probably dumped and my vet who is quite old saw her a week later and said he has never seen nipples that big and long she still had milk when i got her it has now been a little over two months and i am glad to say that they have gone way down and i thought they never would the vet said they will never be tiny again but with the combination of time no longer nursing and the fact that she has now been spayed they will and have greatly gone down to where she no longer has that swinging going on underneath or the huge nipples at first when i would walk her everyone asked if she had just had puppies and now very few people ask you can see her pictures under my questions she's the little one good luck it will get better Dog Breastfeeding Guinea pig Housebreaking Pet skunk Breast Nipple Dobermann Golden Retriever Platypus Nipple piercing Dog training Tasmanian Devil Domestic rabbit Ferret Great Dane American Pit Bull Terrier Nintendogs House Mouse Hormone replacement therapy (trans) Internal ballistics American Eskimo Dog Kitten Milk Episodes of Lost (Season 1) Ren and Stimpy Stomach cancer Pit bull Humphrey Bogart Irish Wolfhound Shetland Sheepdog German Shepherd Dog Docking Dog breed Seabird Maltese (dog) Equine conformation Pekingese Gong Breast fetishism Panama Canal Acne Working dog Swift Vets and POWs for Truth Brassiere Janet Jackson Dog show Greyhound Garfield Feral cat Jennifer Lopez Chocolate Mixed-breed dog Battle of the Bulge Richard Chase Rottweiler Neighbours Manx (cat) Luck Game show Eddie Guerrero Body piercing Toilet humour Hamster Human penis size Korea Jindo Dog Kammerlader Second Battle of the Atlantic Skye